text: The 1950 New Mexico gubernatorial election took place on November 7, 1950, in order to elect the Governor of New Mexico. Incumbent Democrat Thomas J. Mabry was term-limited, and could not run for a third consecutive term. ==General election== ===Results=== ==References== 1950 gubernatorial New Mexico Category:November 1950 events
title: 1950 New Mexico gubernatorial election
